column2: lowelab - These are from the Lowe Lab's website on tRNA numbers in genomes (accessed Jan 2015)
codonR - These are the trna numbers from the original file distributed with codonR (ecolik12.trna)
"codon" really means codon. Take the reverse complement if you want to get the anticodon (i.e. how tRNAs are typically thought of)
